          </li>
          <li> 
            <p>
              Now list all ordered pairs in the relation.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </statement>
      <answer>
        <p>
          The complete listing of the relation is:
          <m>
            R= \{(1,1),(1,2),(1,3),(1,4),(1,5),(1,6),(1,7),(1,8),(1,9),(1,10),\\(2,2),(2,4),(2,6),(2,8),(2,10),(3,3),(3,6),(3,9),(4,4),(4,8),\\(5,5),(5,10),(6,6),(7,7),(8,8),(9,9),(10,10)\}
